title.rendered: Automate, Delegate and Eliminate with Will Christensen from DataAutomation

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 15:31 — 14.2MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Podcast (10k-podcast): Play in new window | Download (Duration: 15:31 — 14.2MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | TuneIn | RSS

Will Christensen is the founder and CEO of DataAutomation, a software company that focuses on integration and automation for small and large scale businesses.

Automation leads us to quick processing of large amounts of tasks and reduces turnaround time. It allows you to achieve more results with hardly any efforts.

Will Christensen will be teaching about the three different processes that will help you on your automation journey.

 

You’ll learn about:

  • How they started their own podcast 
  • Why it is important to manage your FBA process 
  • The significance of choosing what’s working, eliminate what isn’t working
  • The importance of defining what success looks like

Next Steps:

www.dataautomation.com and use contact form

mention “Amazing FBA”/10K Collective Podcast

 

Interviews Related to Automation:

  • Multichannel Campaign Management with Rytis Lauris
  • Omni Channel Marketing with Rytis Lauris
  • Following up on Amazon Reviews with Automated Email with Henson Wu

Other Interviews from Will Christensen:

  • The E-myth Revisited & the E-Commerce Seller with Will Christensen from DataAutomation.com
  • Process Tools for Amazon Sellers with Will Christensen from DataAutomation

Watch Automate, Delegate and Eliminate with Will Christensen
